room_title: Escape room "The Second Floor" by No Way Out in St. Louis
room_description: Your team has been selected for a very important mission. I.B. Stealing & her team of art thieves have turned the second floor of the building into a black market auction. The proceeds from these auctions provide funding for criminal activity all around the world. Your mission is to go upstairs and recover the money that this crime-ridden group has made from selling black market items. Move quickly, you only have one hour before Stealingâ€™s team comes back to check on the property. Are you up for the challenge?
